schlumberger nv schlumberger ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Construction Related Pro Svcs
Schlumberger N.V. (Schlumberger Limited) was founded in 1992. The company's line of business includes providing professional architectural services.




