                    Listen to the Second-Quarter 2017 Results Conference Call Replay
                

Schlumberger hosted a conference call to discuss second-quarter 2017 results.

                    Details...
                














                    Schlumberger and Weatherford to Form OneStim Joint Venture
                

 Joint venture to deliver completions products and services for the development of unconventional resource plays in the United States and Canada land markets.

                    Learn more...
                














                    2016 InteractiveAnnual Report
                

Discover how Schlumberger provides the technology and business models that improve efficiency and enable unprecedented levels of collaboration and integration across the full spectrum of E&P technology—from pore to pipeline.

                    Read more...
                














                    Complete Cased Hole Answers from a Single Tool 
                

Introducing Pulsar multifunction spectroscopy service for stand-alone cased hole formation evaluation—including TOC for unconventional reservoirs—and reservoir saturation monitoring. 

                    Read more...
                














                    Map Reservoir Fluids… All in Real Time, While Drilling
                

SpectraSphere fluid-mapping-while drilling service is the industry’s first to provide high-quality formation pressure measurements, in situ downhole fluid analysis, and representative fluid sampling—in real time, while drilling.

                    Learn more...
                














                    Don’t Miss Our Comprehensive Technical Program
                

More than 140 talks covering the full E&P lifecycle including reservoir characterization, drilling, production, and processing.

                    Learn more...
                




















